CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of two men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence signing documents, and four women, including Alma Illery seated on right, gathered behind table, in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
